[heading Deep Index]

[alert warning
  This service is currently in beta test and active on the BNB Smart Chain (BSC),
  Fantom (FTM), Polygon (MATIC) and Avalanche (AVAX) testnets and mainnets, and the
  Ethereum Goerli testnet. If you need any help don't hesitate to join our communities
  or send us an email at [link mailto:support@kenshi.io support@kenshi.io].]

The Kenshi Deep Index service consists of multiple services for retrieving, querying
and processing blockchain data:

[list 
  [: [bold Sync] can be used to retrieve, store and index data on the Kenshi database clusters.]
  [: [bold GraphQL and MQL] can be used to query, search and retrieve synced blockchain data in your apps.]
  [: [bold Reverse-API] can be used to get notifications about new blockchain events on your HTTP endpoints.]]

